{
  "sn1.35:0.1": "Saṃyutta Nikāya 1 ",
  "sn1.35:0.2": "4. Satullapakāyikavagga ",
  "sn1.35:0.3": "35. Ujjhānasaññisutta ",
  "sn1.35:1.1": "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. ",
  "sn1.35:1.2": "Atha kho sambahulā ujjhānasaññikā devatāyo abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇā kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā vehāsaṃ aṭṭhaṃsu. ",
  "sn1.35:1.3": "Vehāsaṃ ṭhitā kho ekā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: ",
  "sn1.35:2.1": "“Aññathā santamattānaṃ, ",
  "sn1.35:2.2": "aññathā yo pavedaye; ",
  "sn1.35:2.3": "Nikacca kitavasseva, ",
  "sn1.35:2.4": "bhuttaṃ theyyena tassa taṃ. ",
  "sn1.35:3.1": "Yañhi kayirā tañhi vade, ",
  "sn1.35:3.2": "yaṃ na kayirā na taṃ vade; ",
  "sn1.35:3.3": "Akarontaṃ bhāsamānaṃ, ",
  "sn1.35:3.4": "parijānanti paṇḍitā”ti. ",
  "sn1.35:4.1": "“Na yidaṃ bhāsitamattena, ",
  "sn1.35:4.2": "ekantasavanena vā; ",
  "sn1.35:4.3": "Anukkamitave sakkā, ",
  "sn1.35:4.4": "yāyaṃ paṭipadā daḷhā; ",
  "sn1.35:4.5": "Yāya dhīrā pamuccanti, ",
  "sn1.35:4.6": "jhāyino mārabandhanā. ",
  "sn1.35:5.1": "Na ve dhīrā pakubbanti, ",
  "sn1.35:5.2": "viditvā lokapariyāyaṃ; ",
  "sn1.35:5.3": "Aññāya nibbutā dhīrā, ",
  "sn1.35:5.4": "tiṇṇā loke visattikan”ti. ",
  "sn1.35:6.1": "Atha kho tā devatāyo pathaviyaṃ patiṭṭhahitvā bhagavato pādesu sirasā nipatitvā bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ: ",
  "sn1.35:6.2": "“accayo no, bhante, accagamā yathābālaṃ yathāmūḷhaṃ yathāakusalaṃ, yā mayaṃ bhagavantaṃ āsādetabbaṃ amaññimhā. ",
  "sn1.35:6.3": "Tāsaṃ no, bhante, bhagavā accayaṃ accayato paṭiggaṇhātu āyatiṃ saṃvarāyā”ti. ",
  "sn1.35:6.4": "Atha kho bhagavā sitaṃ pātvākāsi. ",
  "sn1.35:6.5": "Atha kho tā devatāyo bhiyyoso mattāya ujjhāyantiyo vehāsaṃ abbhuggañchuṃ. ",
  "sn1.35:6.6": "Ekā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: ",
  "sn1.35:7.1": "“Accayaṃ desayantīnaṃ, ",
  "sn1.35:7.2": "yo ce na paṭigaṇhati; ",
  "sn1.35:7.3": "Kopantaro dosagaru, ",
  "sn1.35:7.4": "sa veraṃ paṭimuñcatī”ti. ",
  "sn1.35:8.1": "“Accayo ce na vijjetha, ",
  "sn1.35:8.2": "nocidhāpagataṃ siyā; ",
  "sn1.35:8.3": "Verāni na ca sammeyyuṃ, ",
  "sn1.35:8.4": "kenīdha kusalo siyā”ti. ",
  "sn1.35:9.1": "“Kassaccayā na vijjanti, ",
  "sn1.35:9.2": "kassa natthi apāgataṃ; ",
  "sn1.35:9.3": "Ko na sammohamāpādi, ",
  "sn1.35:9.4": "ko ca dhīro sadā sato”ti. ",
  "sn1.35:10.1": "“Tathāgatassa buddhassa, ",
  "sn1.35:10.2": "sabbabhūtānukampino; ",
  "sn1.35:10.3": "Tassaccayā na vijjanti, ",
  "sn1.35:10.4": "tassa natthi apāgataṃ; ",
  "sn1.35:10.5": "So na sammohamāpādi, ",
  "sn1.35:10.6": "sova dhīro sadā satoti. ",
  "sn1.35:11.1": "Accayaṃ desayantīnaṃ, ",
  "sn1.35:11.2": "yo ce na paṭigaṇhati; ",
  "sn1.35:11.3": "Kopantaro dosagaru, ",
  "sn1.35:11.4": "sa veraṃ paṭimuñcati; ",
  "sn1.35:11.5": "Taṃ veraṃ nābhinandāmi, ",
  "sn1.35:11.6": "paṭiggaṇhāmi voccayan”ti. "
}